
### How to Trade OCUR

**UR.Land** uses **OCUR**, a standard issue ETH ERC-20 token, as both its stock and currency. More details can be found [here](https://etherscan.io/token/0xCcaB679860B1017589239BCeEEabe5CD45965aFc).


<br/><br/>
To exchange, copy the address,

<div style="text-align:center;">
<a onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('0xCcaB679860B1017589239BCeEEabe5CD45965aFc');M.toast({html: 'Address copied.'});" class="waves-effect waves-light btn">Copy&nbsp;&nbsp;‚úÇÔ∏è</a></div>
<br/><br/>

...then use the [Uniswap](https://app.uniswap.org) exchange to transfer the tokens.


You can also purchase physical/digital **OCUR** packs [here](https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/62652367444291733483705976494538757758952482544655308357132040313142580873668) and the **OCUR** will be transferred to your wallet automatically.

#### Concept of LOCUR

**LOCUR** represents *local* **OCUR**, and represents any **OCUR** sent to UR.Land's official site wallet.

Use **LOCUR** to access the site's features without a *deed domain*.

To purchase, either,


- select the **LOCUR** üè† icon in the ü™ô **Wallet** menu
- send **OCUR** directly with your wallet app, to the following address:

